{
  "stem": "16345.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was 14 years old, and the only schools I had been to besides first and second grade were the schools of hard knocks-- which I learned a lot, but nothing-- not subjects that a 14-year-old should learn.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we hopped the train and went to Rome.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is a really funny story, because in Rome there was a rumor-- now, in those days I had acquired some other clothing besides my striped pants and jacket-- there was a rumor in Rome that the Vatican was giving out money.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Italians made great ice cream.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now in Germany, everything was lawless.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You wanted something, you went and-- and got it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, if-- if you wanted a chicken, you went to a farm and if you hunted-- I-- I used to try and shoot with my-- with my little bitty gun, I tried to shoot chickens.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never hit anyone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But if you grabbed-- if you got a hold of a chicken, you wrung its neck, and you cooked it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you had chicken.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in Italy there were-- there was law and order, more or less.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a rumor that in the Vatican they were giving out money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was only one thing-- you had to convert.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, well, for an ice cream, why not?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were giving everybody 10,000 or 15,000 lire, which was the equivalent, I think, of a quarter, but you could get a great big ice cream cone for that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went and converted, and I got me an ice cream.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was the first ice cream I tasted in five years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then it tasted so good I wanted to go convert again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They cut down on the-- on the amount of money.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
